To find Maximum value in an array

public class max {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {1,3,8,12,11};
        System.out.print(max(arr));
    }

    static int max(int[] arr){
        int maxval = arr[0];
        for(int i = 1;i<arr.length;i++){
            if(arr[i]> maxval){
                maxval = arr[i];
            }
            

        }
        return maxval;
        

    }
}

Output : 12
